<para style="q1">

<verse number="39" style="v" />Salvation of the righteous comes from Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">he protects them in the times of trouble.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="40" style="v" />Yahweh helps them and rescues them.</para>

<para style="q1">He rescues them from evil men and saves them</para>

<para style="q1">because they have taken refuge in him.</para>
